\c 14
\s UJowabi wenza icebo lokubuyisa uAbisalomu
\p
\v 1 UJowabi indodana kaZeruya wasenanzelela ukuthi inhliziyo yenkosi ikuAbisalomu\x + 13.39.\x*.
\v 2 UJowabi wasethumela eThekhowa\x + 23.26. 1 Lan. 27.9. 2 Lan. 11.6. 20.20. Neh. 3.5,27. Jer. 6.1. Amos 1.1. 1 Lan. 2.24. 4.5.\x* ukuthi alande khona owesifazana ohlakaniphileyo, wathi kuye: Ake uzitshaye olilayo, ake ugqoke izigqoko zokulila, ungazigcobi ngamafutha, kodwa ube njengowesifazana oselilele ofileyo insuku ezinengi\x + Ruthe 3.3.\x*.
\v 3 Ungene enkosini, ukhulume kuyo ngalindlela. UJowabi wasefaka amazwi emlonyeni wakhe\x + 14.19. Eks. 4.15.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Lapho owesifazana umThekhowa ekhuluma enkosini, wathi mbo ngobuso bakhe emhlabathini, wakhothama, wathi: Siza, nkosi\x + 1.2. 1 Sam. 20.41.\x*!
\v 5 Inkosi yasisithi kuye: Ulani? Yena wasesithi: Sibili\x + 12.1.\x*, ngingumfazi ongumfelokazi, lendoda yami yafa.
\v 6 Njalo incekukazi yakho yayilamadodana amabili, alwa womabili egangeni; kwakungelamlamuli phakathi kwawo; enye yasitshaya enye, yayibulala\x + Gen. 17.19. Ezra 10.13.\x*.
\v 7 Khangela-ke, usendo lonke seluvukele incekukazi yakho, bathi: Nikela lowo owatshaya umfowabo wambulala, ukuthi simbulale ngenxa yempilo yomfowabo ambulalayo\x + Mat. 21.38.\x*, sichithe lendlalifa. Ngalokho bacitshe ilahle lami eliseleyo\x + Mat. 21.38.\x*, ukuze bangatshiyeli indoda yami ibizo lensali ebusweni bomhlaba\x + Gen. 45.7.\x*.
\v 8 Inkosi yasisithi kowesifazana: Yana endlini yakho; mina-ke ngizalaya ngawe.
\v 9 Owesifazana umThekhowa wasesithi enkosini: Nkosi yami, nkosi, icala kalibe phezu kwami laphezu kwendlu kababa\x + 1 Sam. 25.24. Gen. 27.13. Mat. 27.25.\x*; kodwa inkosi lesihlalo sayo sobukhosi kube msulwa\x + 3.28,29. 1 Kho. 2.33.\x*.
\v 10 Inkosi yasisithi: Okhuluma \add ulutho\add* kuwe, umlethe kimi, njalo kayikuphinda akuthinte futhi.
\v 11 Wasesithi: Inkosi ake ikhumbule iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wayo ukuthi umphindiseli wegazi angabe esachitha, hlezi bachithe indodana yami\x + Nani 35.19,21. Dute. 19.12.\x*. Yasisithi: Kuphila kukaJehova\x + Ruthe 3.13.\x*, kakuyikuwela emhlabathini olulodwa unwele lwendodana yakho\x + 1 Sam. 14.45.\x*.
\v 12 Owesifazana wasesithi: Incekukazi yakho ake ikhulume ilizwi enkosini yami inkosi. Yasisithi: Khuluma.
\v 13 Owesifazana wasesithi: Pho, unakaneleni okunje ngabantu bakaNkulunkulu\x + Hlu. 20.2.\x*? Ngokukhuluma lindaba inkosi injengolecala, ngokuthi inkosi kayibuyisanga oxotshiweyo wayo\x + 13.37,38.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba kumele sife, sinjengamanzi achithekele emhlabathini angabuthwanga\x + 1 Sam. 7.6.\x*; kodwa uNkulunkulu kayikususa impilo, kodwa uzacabanga amacebo ukuthi angalahli kuye oxotshiweyo\x + Nani 35.15,25,28.\x*.
\v 15 Ngakho-ke, njengoba ngizile ukukhuluma linto enkosini, inkosi yami, \add ku\add*ngoba abantu bangesabisile; incekukazi yakho yasisithi: Khathesi ngizakhuluma lenkosi; mhlawumbe inkosi izakwenza ilizwi lencekukazi yayo.
\v 16 Ngoba inkosi izakuzwa, ukukhulula incekukazi yayo esandleni somuntu \add ofuna\add* ukuchitha mina kanye lendodana yami elifeni likaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Sam. 26.19.\x*.
\v 17 Incekukazi yakho yasisithi: Akuthi ilizwi lenkosi yami, inkosi, libe ngelokuthula, ngoba njengengilosi kaNkulunkulu, injalo inkosi yami, inkosi, ukuzwa okubi lokuhle. Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho kayibe lawe\x + 14.20. 1 Sam. 29.9.\x*.
\v 18 Inkosi yasiphendula yathi kowesifazana: Ake ungangifihleli indaba engizayibuza kuwe. Owesifazana wasesithi: Ake ikhulume inkosi yami, inkosi.
\v 19 Inkosi yasisithi: Isandla sikaJowabi silawe yini kukho konke lokhu? Owesifazana wasephendula wathi: Kuphila komphefumulo wakho, nkosi yami\x + 1 Sam. 1.26.\x*, nkosi, isibili kakho ongaya ngakwesokunene langakwesokhohlo asuke lakuyiphi into inkosi yami, inkosi, eyikhulumileyo\x + Mika 6.10.\x*; ngoba inceku yakho uJowabi, yona yangilaya, yiyo eyafunza incekukazi yakho wonke lamazwi.
\v 20 Inceku yakho uJowabi iyenzile linto ukuthi iphendule ukuma kwendaba. Njalo inkosi yami ihlakaniphile njengenhlakanipho yengilosi kaNkulunkulu, ukwazi konke okusemhlabeni\x + 14.3.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Inkosi yasisithi kuJowabi: Khangela khathesi, ngenzile lindaba; ngakho hamba ubuyise umfana uAbisalomu.
\v 22 UJowabi wasesithi mbo ngobuso emhlabathini, wakhothama, wayibusisa inkosi; uJowabi wasesithi: Lamuhla inceku yakho iyazi ukuthi ngithole umusa emehlweni akho, nkosi yami, nkosi, ngokuthi inkosi yenzile indaba yenceku yayo.
\v 23 Wasesuka uJowabi, waya eGeshuri, wamletha uAbisalomu eJerusalema\x + 14.32. 13.38.\x*.
\v 24 Inkosi yasisithi: Kaphendukele endlini yakhe, angaboni ubuso bami. Ngakho uAbisalomu waphendukela endlini yakhe, kabonanga ubuso benkosi.
\p
\v 25 KoIsrayeli wonke-ke kwakungelamuntu onjengoAbisalomu ukudunyiswa kakhulu ngobuhle; kwakungelasici kuye kusukela kungaphansi yonyawo lwakhe kuze kufike enkanda yakhe\x + Isa. 1.6.\x*.
\v 26 Nxa ephuca ikhanda lakhe\x + Hez. 44.20.\x* - ngoba kwakusithi ekupheleni kwawo wonke umnyaka aliphuce, ngoba zazinzima kuye, ngakho waliphuca\x + Eks. 13.10.\x* - walinganisa inwele zekhanda lakhe, amashekeli angamakhulu amabili ngesilinganiso senkosi.
\v 27 Kwasekuzalelwa uAbisalomu amadodana amathathu lendodakazi eyodwa, obizo layo lalinguTamari\x + 18.18.\x*; wayengowesifazana omuhle ebukeka\x + Gen. 12.11.\x*.
\p
\v 28 UAbisalomu wasehlala eJerusalema iminyaka emibili epheleleyo, kabonanga ubuso benkosi\x + 13.23.\x*.
\v 29 UAbisalomu wasethumela kuJowabi ukuthi amthume enkosini; kodwa kavumanga ukuza kuye. Waphinda wathumela ngokwesibili, kodwa kavumanga ukuza.
\v 30 Wasesithi ezincekwini zakhe: Bonani, isabelo sikaJowabi siseceleni kwesami, njalo \w ulebhali\w** lapho; hambani lisithungele ngomlilo. Izinceku zikaAbisalomu zasezithungela isabelo ngomlilo.
\v 31 Wasesuka uJowabi weza kuAbisalomu endlini, wathi kuye: Izinceku zakho zithungeleleni isabelo esingesami ngomlilo?
\v 32 UAbisalomu wasesithi kuJowabi: Khangela, ngithumele kuwe ngisithi: Woza lapha, ukuze ngikuthume enkosini, ukuthi: Ngibuyeleni ngisuka eGeshuri? Bekukuhle kimi ukuthi ngabe ngilokhu ngikhonale. Ngakho-ke kangibone ubuso benkosi; njalo uba kulecala kimi, kayingibulale\x + 1 Sam. 20.8.\x*.
\v 33 Ngakho uJowabi weza enkosini, wayitshela; isimbizile uAbisalomu weza enkosini, wayikhothamela ngobuso bakhe emhlabathini, phambi kwenkosi; inkosi yasimanga uAbisalomu\x + 15.5. 19.39. 20.9. Gen. 29.13. 31.55. 33.4. 45.15. Eks. 18.7. Luka 15.20. 22.47.\x*.